high_descs: Pick up a sponge from the rack
Wash the sponge in the sink
Put the sponge in the bath tub
anns.task_desc: Wash and place a sponge in a bath tub

high_descs: Turn right and head to the toilet then turn left and head to the cart in front of the window
Pick up the sponge from the bottom of the cart
Turn left, then turn left, then turn right and go to the bathtub, then turn right, then right and go to the sink
Put the sponge in the sink and turn on the water, then take the sponge from the sink
Turn around to face the bathtub
Put the sponge in the bathtub
anns.task_desc: Put a clean wet sponge in the bathtub

high_descs: Walk across the room to the steel rack.
Turn left, walk across the room to the tub, and turn around to face the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water, and pick up the sponge.
Turn around to face the tub.
Put the sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge in the tub.
